    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行行长斯图纳拉斯认为 2024 年再降息两次是“合理的”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/ecb-s-stournaras-sees-two-more-rate-cuts-in-2024-as-reasonable</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行管理委员会委员亚尼斯·斯图纳拉斯 (Yannis Stournaras) 表示，近期通胀和经济扩张数据强化了欧洲央行进一步降息的论据，今年再降息两次左右较为合适。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/ecb-s-stournaras-sees-two-more-rate-cuts-in-2024-as-reasonable</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 16:31:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
